This paper focuses on machine learning in wireless edge networks, which involves topics such as privacy, communication efficiency, and distributed learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
